string.name: rules_info
string.value: Tic-Tac-Toe is a simple and fun game for two players. It is played on a 3 x 3 grid. Players take turns placing their Mark, X or O, on an open square in the grid. The first player to make three of their own mark in a row vertically, horizontally, or diagonally wins the game.

string.name: rules_info1
string.value: Tic-Tac-Toe is a zero-sum game, which means that if both players are playing their best, the game will end in a tie.
